{
    "id": "",
    "module_type": "pid",
    "category": "应用/PID控制器",
    "name": "PID控制器 (PID Controller)",
    "description": "PID控制器是一个典型的闭环控制模块，用于将温度、压力等被控量稳定在设定值。它比较设定值与反馈值的偏差，通过比例(P)、积分(I)、微分(D)运算输出控制量。该模块支持正/反向作用、死区设置、输出限幅以及多种停机/无效时的输出模式。",
    "keywords": [
        "PID",
        "温度",
        "压力",
        "闭环控制",
        "比例积分微分",
        "过程控制"
    ],
    "usage_guides": [
        "输入端至少包括：使能信号、设定值(SV)、反馈值(PV)。",
        "当[使能]端口输入为“不使能”（0）时，模块[输出值]根据[禁止时输出]的设定输出相应的值。当[使能]端口输入为“使能”（1）时，模块在上一刻[输出值]的基础上开始运算。",
        "当[运算方向]为正向时：当 设定值 ＞ 输入+死区 时，“输出”逐渐增大。当 设定值 ＜ 输入-死区 时，“输出”逐渐减少。",
        "当[运算方向]为反向时：当 设定值 ＞ 输入+死区 时，“输出”逐渐减少。当 设定值 ＜ 输入-死区 时，“输出”逐渐增大。",
        "“输出”的值限制在[输出下限值 , 输出上限值]范围内。",
        "可以通过设置inputsOption，开放该参数的输入引脚，以便在运行期动态修改PID参数或其它参数。"
    ],
    "parameters_schema": {
        "pidMode": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "PID运算方向。如果对该项启用动态输入，当输入值为 0 表示正向运算，输入值为 非0 表示反向运算。",
            "enum": ["direct", "reverse"],
            "default": "direct"
        },
        "proportional": {
            "type": "number",
            "description": "比例增益(P)。",
            "default": 20
        },
        "integral": {
            "type": "number",
            "description": "积分增益(I)。",
            "default": 2
        },
        "derivative": {
            "type": "number",
            "description": "微分增益(D)。",
            "default": 0
        },
        "highPidOutLimit": {
            "type": "number",
            "description": "PID计算输出的上限值。",
            "default": 0
        },
        "lowPidOutLimit": {
            "type": "number",
            "description": "PID计算输出的下限值。",
            "default": 0
        },
        "interval": {
            "type": "integer",
            "description": "PID运算的时间间隔（秒），是一个大于0的整数。",
            "minimum": 1,
            "default": 60
        },
        "deadBand": {
            "type": "number",
            "description": "死区范围。偏差在该范围内时不调整输出，是一个非负整数。",
            "minimum": 0,
            "default": 0
        },
        "disabledOutValue": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "不使能（禁止）时的输出模式。max: 输出值为[上限值]；min: 输出值为[下限值]；zero: 输出值为0；hold: 输出值为[不使能前一刻的值]。",
            "enum": ["hold", "max", "min", "zero"],
            "default": "hold"
        },
        "inputsCount": {
            "type": "integer",
            "description": "动态输入时输入端口数量（范围 3~12）。",
            "minimum": 3,
            "maximum": 12,
            "default": 3
        },
        "inputsOption": {
            "type": "string array",
            "description": "选择是否要对某些参数启用外部输入端口，以便在运行期动态修改这些参数。（可以多选）",
            "enum": ["pidMode", "proportional", "integral", "derivative", "highPidOutLimit", "lowPidOutLimit", "interval", "deadBand"],
            "default": "[]"
        }
    },
    "ports_definition": {
        "inputs": [
        {
            "index": 0,
            "label": "使能",
            "type": "boolean",
            "description": "PID运行的使能控制。0：不使能；1：使能。",
            "condition": "always"
        },
        {
            "index": 1,
            "label": "设定值",
            "type": "number",
            "description": "目标设定值。",
            "condition": "always"
        },
        {
            "index": 2,
            "label": "输入",
            "type": "number",
            "description": "受控目标测量反馈值。",
            "condition": "always"
        },
        {
            "index": 3,
            "label": "比例增益",
            "type": "number",
            "description": "PID的比例增益。",
            "condition": "inputsOption 中包含'proportional'"
        },
        {
            "index": 4,
            "label": "积分增益",
            "type": "number",
            "description": "PID的积分增益。",
            "condition": "inputsOption 中包含'integral'"
        },
        {
            "index": 5,
            "label": "微分增益",
            "type": "number",
            "description": "PID的微分增益。",
            "condition": "inputsOption 中包含'derivative'"
        },
        {
            "index": 6,
            "label": "输出上限值",
            "type": "number",
            "description": "PID允许输出的上限值。",
            "condition": "inputsOption 中包含'highPidOutLimit'"
        },
        {
            "index": 7,
            "label": "输出下限值",
            "type": "number",
            "description": "PID允许输出的下限值。",
            "condition": "inputsOption 中包含'lowPidOutLimit'"
        },
        {
            "index": 8,
            "label": "运算间隔(S)",
            "type": "integer",
            "description": "PID运算的时间间隔，单位秒（s）。最小值为1秒。",
            "condition": "inputsOption 中包含'interval'"
        },
        {
            "index": 9,
            "label": "死区",
            "type": "non_negative_integer",
            "description": "PID运算的死区DB。",
            "condition": "inputsOption 中包含'deadBand'"
        },
        {
            "index": 10,
            "label": "运算方向",
            "type": "boolean",
            "description": "PID的运行模式，对应关系如下：0：正向PID；1：反向PID。",
            "condition": "inputsOption 中包含'pidMode'"
        }
        ],
        "outputs": [
        {
            "index": 0,
            "label": "输出",
            "type": "integer",
            "description": "运算结果。执行单元调节目标值。",
            "condition": "always"
        }
        ]
    },
    "template_json": [
        {
            "id": "{{__GEN_ID__}}",
            "z": "{{__FLOW_ID__}}",
            "type": "pid",
            "name": "PID",
            "inputs": "{{inputsCount}}",
            "outputs": 1,
            "pidMode": "{{pidMode}}",
            "proportional": "{{proportional}}",
            "integral": "{{integral}}",
            "derivative": "{{derivative}}",
            "highPidOutLimit": "{{highPidOutLimit}}",
            "lowPidOutLimit": "{{lowPidOutLimit}}",
            "interval": "{{interval}}",
            "deadBand": "{{deadBand}}",
            "disabledOutValue": "{{disabledOutValue}}",
            "proportionalChecked": false,
            "integralChecked": false,
            "derivativeChecked": false,
            "highPidOutLimitChecked": false,
            "lowPidOutLimitChecked": false,
            "intervalChecked": false,
            "deadBandChecked": false,
            "outOfService": 0,
            "outOfServiceValue": 0,
            "inputsOption": "{{inputsOptionArray}}",
            "inputsOptionCache": [],
            "x": "{{xCoord}}",
            "y": "{{yCoord}}",
            "wires": "{{wiresArray}}"
        }
    ]
}